'''Architecture and Design Scotland''', styled '''Architecture+DesignScotland''' (A&DS; {{lang-gd|Ailtearachd is Dealbhadh na h-Alba}}), is an [[executive non-departmental public body]] of the [[Scottish Government]]. 

It was established in 2005 to provide advice to the government and bodies involved in commissioning, designing and regulating new buildings and places.

